data.text:
Wolf Prize

Since 1978, five to six Wolf prizes have been awarded annually in the Sciences. Prize fields comprise Agriculture, Chemistry, Mathematics, Medicine and Physics. In the Arts, the prize rotates annually among Architecture, Painting, and Sculpture.
